40|$|We {{determine}} the <b>greatest</b> <b>lower</b> <b>bounds</b> on the transverse Ricci curvature of compact toric Sasaki manifolds with positive basic first Chern class {{and with the}} first Chern class of the contact bundle being trivial. This is based on Wang-Zhu's and Futaki-Ono-Wang's works, and is an analogue of C. Li's work on toric Fano manifolds. Comment: 10 page...|$|R
